{"tid":1382730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武必需謹記七個字：上得山多終遇虎","createTime":"2019-07-29T14:10:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T00:10:31.000Z","uid":271284,"like":154,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"31890e92293bab457abf00766f0bf1322ad5aa4a","tid":1382730,"uid":271284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:10:36.000Z","msg":"依家成個連登，大部分tg，蘋果，立場，以致整個泛民都為緊勇武護航，好聽講就係萬眾一心，但一唔小心就好容易Total loss<br />\n<br />\n我地依家既前線行動其實基於一個唔太可靠既假設：警察會按已知規則行事<br />\n<br />\n如果佢突然使用不合比例武力，或者封曬所有地鐵站加四面包抄唔比你撤退呢？咁你可以點？投訴警察？？由上星期開始我地連講be water都會屌，但我地真係咁有信心咩？<br />\n<br />\n我地依家好似長買大熱咁，每次贏幾%...<br />\n<br />\n但記住我地只要一次被團滅我地就玩完"},{"pid":"4051167feabf9cd3f64c4ae971a8f049351ea5b6","tid":1382730,"uid":271284,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:23:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21004bda0cc69dbf3f7d997518b15d26915d664f","tid":1382730,"uid":271284,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:28:07.000Z","msg":"理性討論已經無market<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04cc43453ae09fdd222ede37167cec91f4387a1b","tid":1382730,"uid":271284,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:40:59.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯反對派前日被團滅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n莫斯科示威抗議反對派不獲資格參選　被捕人數增至逾千人<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/即時國際/357132/莫斯科示威抗議反對派不獲資格參選-被捕人數增至逾千人\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%2F357132%2F%E8%8E%AB%E6%96%AF%E7%A7%91%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E6%B4%BE%E4%B8%8D%E7%8D%B2%E8%B3%87%E6%A0%BC%E5%8F%83%E9%81%B8-%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E4%BA%BA%E6%95%B8%E5%A2%9E%E8%87%B3%E9%80%BE%E5%8D%83%E4%BA%BA&d=eDToqso6oamdFbclmZMiiQOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=63b1328d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/即時國際/357132/莫斯科示威抗議反對派不獲資格參選-被捕人數增至逾千人</a>"},{"pid":"da034